        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued May 8 at 5:57AM CDT by NWS Midland/Odessa TX</headline>
        <description>At 556 AM CDT, Doppler radar was tracking a strong thunderstorm near
Crane, moving northeast at 35 mph.

HAZARD...Half inch hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Minor hail damage to vegetation is possible.

Locations impacted include...
Crane and Crane County Airport.
</description>
        <instruction>If outdoors, consider seeking shelter inside a building.</instruction>
